### ============================================
### API REST - Spring Security Tutorial
### ============================================
### Credenciales:
### - usuario:password123 → dXN1YXJpbzpwYXNzd29yZDEyMw==
### - admin:admin123 → YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=
### ============================================

### -----------------------------------------
### ENDPOINTS PÚBLICOS (sin autenticación)
### -----------------------------------------

### Endpoint público - No requiere login
GET http://localhost:8080/api/public
Accept: application/json

###

### -----------------------------------------
### ENDPOINTS PROTEGIDOS (requieren autenticación)
### -----------------------------------------

### Endpoint privado - Usuario normal
### Usuario: usuario / password123
GET http://localhost:8080/api/private
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic dXN1YXJpbzpwYXNzd29yZDEyMw==

###

### -----------------------------------------
### ENDPOINTS SOLO ADMIN
### -----------------------------------------

### Endpoint admin - Usuario admin
### Usuario: admin / admin123
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4xMjM=

###

### -----------------------------------------
### PRUEBAS DE ACCESO DENEGADO
### -----------------------------------------

### Acceso a /api/private SIN credenciales → 401 Unauthorized
GET http://localhost:8080/api/private
Accept: application/json

###

### Usuario normal intentando acceder a /api/admin → 403 Forbidden
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic dXN1YXJpbzpwYXNzd29yZDEyMw==

###

### -----------------------------------------
### ENDPOINTS WEB (HTML)
### -----------------------------------------

### Página pública
GET http://localhost:8080/public
Accept: text/html

###

### Página privada (requiere autenticación)
GET http://localhost:8080/private
Accept: text/html
Authorization: Basic dXN1YXJpbzpwYXNzd29yZDEyMw==

###

